# 在 **Python** 虛擬環境中安裝包環境


## 創建虛擬環境
```
$ conda create --name HM python=3.8  (HM is virtual enviroment name)
$ conda activate HM	
```

## 安裝所需的python包
```
$ conda install SCons
$ conda install kconfiglib
$ conda uninstall crypto pycryptodome
$ conda install pycryptodome
$ conda install ecdsa
```
## 安裝編譯器和構建工具

- Cross complier : gcc_riscv32-linux-7.3.0.tar.gz
- meta-build     : gn.1523.tar
- build system   : ninja.1.9.0.tar

## 解壓並移動到 HarmonyOS 文件夾下
```
$ echo 'export PATH=~/.local/bin:$PATH' | tee -a ~/.bashrc
$ echo 'export PATH=~/HarmonyOS/gn:$PATH' | tee -a ~/.bashrc
$ echo 'export PATH=~/HarmonyOS/ninja:$PATH' | tee -a ~/.bashrc
$ echo 'export PATH=~/HarmonyOS/gcc_riscv32:$PATH' | tee -a ~/.bashrc
```

## 克隆和編譯硬件
```
$ mkdir ~/HarmonyOS/package_1	        
$ cd ~/HarmonyOS/package_1	        
	(the package is installed under folder package_1)
$ hpm init -t dist					
	(prepare the package environment)
$ hpm i @bearpi/bearpi_hm_nano		
	(Clone the bearpi_hm_nano from internet)
$ hpm dist
```